      "title": "Stalhrim Fur Armor",
      "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Stalhrim_Fur_ArmorCC\">Stalhrim Fur Armor<sup style=\"line-height:1.0\"><a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Creation_Club\" title=\"Skyrim:Creation Club\">CC</a></sup></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Skyrim:Stalhrim&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Stalhrim Fur ArmorCC\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>The <a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Alternative_Armors_-_Stalhrim_Fur\" title=\"Skyrim:Alternative Armors - Stalhrim Fur\">Alternative Armors - Stalhrim Fur</a> <a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Creation_Club\" title=\"Skyrim:Creation Club\">Creation</a> adds another variant of heavy Stalhrim armor based on the style of <i><a href=\"/wiki/Blades:Blades\" title=\"Blades:Blades\">Blades</a></i>. It can be crafted after the completion of <a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Ancient_Ice\" title=\"Skyrim:Ancient Ice\">Ancient Ice</a><sup style=\"line-height:1.0\"><a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Alternative_Armors_-_Stalhrim_Fur\" title=\"Skyrim:Alternative Armors - Stalhrim Fur\">CC</a></sup> (as well as <a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:A_New_Source_of_Stalhrim\" title=\"Skyrim:A New Source of Stalhrim\">A New Source of Stalhrim</a>), and is identical to the regular heavy variant apart from each piece having an additional 2 points of armor rating. This makes the set slightly stronger than <a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Daedric_Armor\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Skyrim:Daedric Armor\">daedric armor</a>, while being considerably lighter.\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:202px;\"><a href=\"/wiki/File:SR-item-Stalhrim_Fur_Armor_Male.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/8/89/SR-item-Stalhrim_Fur_Armor_Male.jpg/200px-SR-item-Stalhrim_Fur_Armor_Male.jpg\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/8/89/SR-item-Stalhrim_Fur_Armor_Male.jpg/300px-SR-item-Stalhrim_Fur_Armor_Male.jpg 1.5x, //images.uesp.net/thumb/8/89/SR-item-Stalhrim_Fur_Armor_Male.jpg/400px-SR-item-Stalhrim_Fur_Armor_Male.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/wiki/File:SR-item-Stalhrim_Fur_Armor_Male.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>A male <a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Nord\" title=\"Skyrim:Nord\">Nord</a> wearing Stalhrim fur armor</div></div></div>\n<table class=\"wikitable sortable striped\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<th rowspan=\"2\" class=\"unsortable\">\n</th>\n<th rowspan=\"2\">Name (<a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Form_ID\" title=\"Skyrim:Form ID\">ID</a>)\n</th>\n<th rowspan=\"2\"><a href=\"/wiki/File:SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_(square).png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Weight\"><img alt=\"Weight\" src=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/2/2d/SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png/22px-SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png\" width=\"22\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/2/2d/SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png/33px-SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png 1.5x, //images.uesp.net/thumb/2/2d/SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png/44px-SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png 2x\" /></a>\n</th>\n<th rowspan=\"2\"><a href=\"/wiki/File:SR-item-Gold-heads.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Value\"><img alt=\"Value\" src=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/5/52/SR-item-Gold-heads.png/22px-SR-item-Gold-heads.png\" width=\"22\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/5/52/SR-item-Gold-heads.png/33px-SR-item-Gold-heads.png 1.5x, //images.uesp.net/thumb/5/52/SR-item-Gold-heads.png/44px-SR-item-Gold-heads.png 2x\" /></a>\n</th>\n<th rowspan=\"2\"><a href=\"/wiki/File:SR-icon-armor-IronShield.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Armor Rating\"><img alt=\"Armor Rating\" src=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/f/f0/SR-icon-armor-IronShield.png/22px-SR-icon-armor-IronShield.png\" width=\"22\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/f/f0/SR-icon-armor-IronShield.png/33px-SR-icon-armor-IronShield.png 1.5x, //images.uesp.net/thumb/f/f0/SR-icon-armor-IronShield.png/44px-SR-icon-armor-IronShield.png 2x\" /></a>\n</th>\n<th style=\"border-left-width:medium; border-left-color:black;\" colspan=\"3\" class=\"unsortable\">Raw Materials\n</th>\n<th style=\"border-left-width:medium; border-left-color:black;\" colspan=\"2\" class=\"unsortable\">Delta\n</th>\n<th colspan=\"2\" class=\"unsortable\">Ratio\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<th style=\"border-left-width:medium; border-left-color:black;\"><a href=\"/wiki/File:SR-icon-misc-Stalhrim.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"SR-icon-misc-Stalhrim.png\" src=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/b/bc/SR-icon-misc-Stalhrim.png/24px-SR-icon-misc-Stalhrim.png\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/b/bc/SR-icon-misc-Stalhrim.png/36px-SR-icon-misc-Stalhrim.png 1.5x, //images.uesp.net/thumb/b/bc/SR-icon-misc-Stalhrim.png/48px-SR-icon-misc-Stalhrim.png 2x\" /></a> Stalhrim\n</th>\n<th><a href=\"/wiki/File:SR-icon-ingot-Quicksilver_Ingot.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"SR-icon-ingot-Quicksilver Ingot.png\" src=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/c/ce/SR-icon-ingot-Quicksilver_Ingot.png/24px-SR-icon-ingot-Quicksilver_Ingot.png\" width=\"24\" height=\"20\" srcset=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/c/ce/SR-icon-ingot-Quicksilver_Ingot.png/36px-SR-icon-ingot-Quicksilver_Ingot.png 1.5x, //images.uesp.net/thumb/c/ce/SR-icon-ingot-Quicksilver_Ingot.png/48px-SR-icon-ingot-Quicksilver_Ingot.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Quicksilver_Ingot\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Skyrim:Quicksilver Ingot\">Quicksilver</a>\n</th>\n<th><a href=\"/wiki/File:SR-icon-misc-LeatherStrips.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"SR-icon-misc-LeatherStrips.png\" src=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/3/3a/SR-icon-misc-LeatherStrips.png/24px-SR-icon-misc-LeatherStrips.png\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/3/3a/SR-icon-misc-LeatherStrips.png/36px-SR-icon-misc-LeatherStrips.png 1.5x, //images.uesp.net/thumb/3/3a/SR-icon-misc-LeatherStrips.png/48px-SR-icon-misc-LeatherStrips.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Leather_Strips\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Skyrim:Leather Strips\">Strips</a>\n</th>\n<th style=\"border-left-width:medium; border-left-color:black;\"><a href=\"/wiki/File:SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_(square).png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Weight\"><img alt=\"Weight\" src=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/2/2d/SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png/22px-SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png\" width=\"22\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/2/2d/SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png/33px-SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png 1.5x, //images.uesp.net/thumb/2/2d/SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png/44px-SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png 2x\" /></a>\n</th>\n<th><a href=\"/wiki/File:SR-item-Gold-heads.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Value\"><img alt=\"Value\" src=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/5/52/SR-item-Gold-heads.png/22px-SR-item-Gold-heads.png\" width=\"22\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/5/52/SR-item-Gold-heads.png/33px-SR-item-Gold-heads.png 1.5x, //images.uesp.net/thumb/5/52/SR-item-Gold-heads.png/44px-SR-item-Gold-heads.png 2x\" /></a>\n</th>\n<th><a href=\"/wiki/File:SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_(square).png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Weight\"><img alt=\"Weight\" src=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/2/2d/SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png/22px-SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png\" width=\"22\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/2/2d/SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png/33px-SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png 1.5x, //images.uesp.net/thumb/2/2d/SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png/44px-SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png 2x\" /></a>\n</th>\n<th><a href=\"/wiki/File:SR-item-Gold-heads.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Value\"><img alt=\"Value\" src=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/5/52/SR-item-Gold-heads.png/22px-SR-item-Gold-heads.png\" width=\"22\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/5/52/SR-item-Gold-heads.png/33px-SR-item-Gold-heads.png 1.5x, //images.uesp.net/thumb/5/52/SR-item-Gold-heads.png/44px-SR-item-Gold-heads.png 2x\" /></a>\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/File:SR-icon-armor-Stalhrim_Fur_Armor.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"SR-icon-armor-Stalhrim Fur Armor.png\" src=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/f/f3/SR-icon-armor-Stalhrim_Fur_Armor.png/48px-SR-icon-armor-Stalhrim_Fur_Armor.png\" width=\"48\" height=\"48\" srcset=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/f/f3/SR-icon-armor-Stalhrim_Fur_Armor.png/72px-SR-icon-armor-Stalhrim_Fur_Armor.png 1.5x, //images.uesp.net/thumb/f/f3/SR-icon-armor-Stalhrim_Fur_Armor.png/96px-SR-icon-armor-Stalhrim_Fur_Armor.png 2x\" /></a>\n</td>\n<td><span id=\"Stalhrim_Fur_Armor\"></span>Stalhrim Fur Armor<br /><span class=\"idall\">(<span class=\"idref\"><span class=\"idcase\">FE</span><a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Form_ID#Creation_Club\" title=\"Skyrim:Form ID\"><span style=\"cursor:help;\" title=\"These three digits vary depending on installed Creations. Click for more details.\">xxx</span></a><span class=\"idcase\">801</span></span>)</span></td>\n<td>38</td>\n<td>2200</td>\n<td>48\n</td>\n<td style=\"border-left-width:medium; border-left-color:black;\">6</td>\n<td>1</td>\n<td>3\n</td>\n<td style=\"border-left-width:medium; border-left-color:black; color:red\">30.7\n</td>\n<td>931\n</td>\n<td style=\"color:red\">5.21\n</td>\n<td>1.73\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/File:SR-icon-armor-Stalhrim_Fur_Boots.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"SR-icon-armor-Stalhrim Fur Boots.png\" src=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/0/07/SR-icon-armor-Stalhrim_Fur_Boots.png/48px-SR-icon-armor-Stalhrim_Fur_Boots.png\" width=\"48\" height=\"48\" srcset=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/0/07/SR-icon-armor-Stalhrim_Fur_Boots.png/72px-SR-icon-armor-Stalhrim_Fur_Boots.png 1.5x, //images.uesp.net/thumb/0/07/SR-icon-armor-Stalhrim